desc_short	-----								Fractured Space is a free-to-play 5-v-5 team-based space MOBA where you control your gigantic capital ship to seize mines and bases for team resources and buffs. The intensity of a shooter combines with deep tactical decision making as you battle over five sectors to finally capture the enemy team's base.							
developer									Edge Case Games Ltd.								
